## 🔀 Two Audiences, Two Paths

::left::

<div class="highlight-box">

### 🤖 Service Access Flow
- Trust binding declared in **IaC** (Git)
- **EKS OIDC** at connect-time · short-lived DB-bound credential
- **Okta not in this path** · no stored passwords

</div>

::right::

<div class="highlight-box">

### 👤 Human Access Flow
- Eligibility lives in **Okta groups**
- **Twingate L3 gate first** · SAML carries group attribute
- 4 cases · steady-state RO · transient JIT (B/C/D)

</div>

<div style="position:absolute;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);bottom:1rem;width:240px;opacity:0.9;pointer-events:none;z-index:5;"><img src="https://i.ibb.co/ZpDBbLrc/img-11.jpg" alt="kids-book accent — robot and human shaking hands" style="width:100%;height:auto;display:block;" /></div>


