## 🔬 Functional View — Three Stakeholder Questions

<CardGrid :cols="3">

<Card3D title="🔒 Security — Blast radius?">

Two trust gates only · compromise bounded to one binding · no element holds both audiences' credentials

</Card3D>

<Card3D title="🔮 Evolution — New DB next year?">

Element graph unchanged · one new adapter inside the Reconciler · D-1 lives below this layer

</Card3D>

<Card3D title="🧑‍💻 Usability — Who learns what?">

Engineers: standing RO for daily reads · JIT only when needed · Officers: IaC PRs · `git log` is the audit

</Card3D>

</CardGrid>

> 🔍 **Observability hook:** Audit Aggregator is the spine · every element emits to it.

<div style="position:absolute;right:1.5rem;bottom:1.5rem;width:120px;opacity:0.95;pointer-events:none;z-index:5;"><img src="https://i.ibb.co/zHsXwfRQ/img-15.jpg" alt="kids-book accent — three heads peering through magnifying glass" style="width:100%;height:auto;display:block;" /></div>


